Sentencas: A novel cobalt-free perovskite oxide La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.9Mo0.1O3-delta (LSFM10) was prepared by a citric acid-nitrate process and investigated as a cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: A novel cobalt-free perovskite La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.9Mo0.1O3-δ cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: It was discovered that the doping with Mo for Fe-site distinctly improved the electrical conductivity of the La0.6Sr0.4FeO3-delta sample.
Titulo: A novel cobalt-free perovskite La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.9Mo0.1O3-δ cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The maximum conductivity of LSFM10 reached 159 S cm(-1) at 300-800 degrees C in air.
Titulo: A novel cobalt-free perovskite La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.9Mo0.1O3-δ cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A single cell with the LSFM10 cathode and the proton-conducting BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-delta (BZCY) electrolyte membrane (similar to 35 mu m thickness) supported by a NiO-BZCY composite anode was fabricated and tested at 500-700 degrees C with H-2 as fuel and air as oxidant.
Titulo: A novel cobalt-free perovskite La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.9Mo0.1O3-δ cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The peak power density of the cell reached 496 mW cm(-2) and the interfacial polarization resistance was 0.15 Omega cm(2) at 700 degrees
Titulo: A novel cobalt-free perovskite La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.9Mo0.1O3-δ cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
A novel cobalt-free perovskite La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.9Mo0.1O3-δ cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The experimental results indicated that La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.9Mo0.1O3-delta is a suitable cathode material for the proton-conducting IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: A novel cobalt-free perovskite La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.9Mo0.1O3-δ cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
